ZH: 马鞍是一种供人们骑马时放置在马背上的装备。
EN: A saddle is a piece of equipment placed on the horse's back for people to ride on.
ZH: 我去农场时试着坐在马鞍上，但是感觉很陌生。
EN: I tried sitting on the saddle when I went to the farm, but it felt very unfamiliar.
ZH: 她在马鞍上矫健地坐着，准备出发骑马。
EN: She sat firmly on the saddle, getting ready to start horseback riding.
ZH: 这个冒险家经历跌落马鞍后重新上马的困难。
EN: This adventurer faced difficulties getting back on the horse after falling off the saddle.
ZH: 在乡村度假时，我在马鞍上欣赏着美丽的风景。
EN: I enjoyed the beautiful scenery while sitting on the saddle during a countryside vacation.
ZH: 她哥哥是一个训练有素的骑手，马鞍是他最重要的工具之一。
EN: Her brother is a skilled rider, and the saddle is one of his most important tools.
ZH: 比赛开始前，选手们会检查一下他们的马鞍是否固定好。
EN: Before the competition starts, the participants will check if their saddles are properly fastened.
ZH: 这个年轻骑手很高兴换上了新的马鞍。
EN: The young rider was happy to change to a new saddle.
ZH: 这种马鞍非常舒适，骑马时不会感到不适。
EN: This type of saddle is very comfortable and won't cause discomfort while riding.
ZH: 骑手们会定期清洁和保养他们的马鞍。
EN: Riders regularly clean and maintain their saddles.
ZH: 这个骑手选择了一个黑色的马鞍来搭配他的马匹。
EN: The rider chose a black saddle to match his horse.
ZH: 他习惯金属马鞍而不是皮革马鞍。
EN: He is accustomed to metal saddles instead of leather ones.
ZH: 马鞍上有一个小口袋，方便骑手放置一些物品。
EN: There is a small pocket on the saddle for riders to store some items.
ZH: 这个牧场的马鞍都是由手工制作的。
EN: The saddles in this ranch are all handmade.
ZH: 对于马术爱好者来说，选择合适的马鞍至关重要。
EN: Choosing the right saddle is crucial for equestrian enthusiasts.
ZH: 骑手们通常会选择舒适且轻便的马鞍。
EN: Riders usually choose comfortable and lightweight saddles.
ZH: 我们需要一些马鞍来准备新骑手的训练。
EN: We need some saddles to prepare for the training of new riders.
ZH: 马鞍的设计需要考虑骑手的体型和对马匹的控制力。
EN: The design of the saddle needs to consider the rider's body shape and control over the horse.
ZH: 这个赛马赛场的场地机构特别照顾了马鞍的舒适度。
EN: The venue organization of this racecourse pays special attention to the comfort of the saddles.
ZH: 新手骑手往往需要一些时间来适应骑马和马鞍。
EN: Beginner riders often need some time to get used to riding and the saddle.
